At the time of writing (2012-01-17) this module just re-implement 
for Sinatra the server-side connector of jqueryFileTree [1] .   

It's strongly modeled on connectors/jqueryFileTree.rb, the CGI example
provided within the package [2]. 

-- 

[1] http://www.abeautifulsite.net/blog/2008/03/jquery-file-tree/

[2] http://labs.abeautifulsite.net/archived/jquery-fileTree/jquery.fileTree-1.01.zip

